發老姣，就叫做包養？可能大家覺得我左膠，過分認真，但我都係想咁多位絲打對自己有信心。絲打們，人一世物一世，最緊要開心。有時候唔使理其他人點諗，因為我哋係唔係都俾人叫&rdquo;臭雞&rdquo;㗎啦，我寧願做隻&rdquo;快樂嘅臭雞&rdquo;。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28acc0036a614b581098d9141597a197ffedb2a6","tid":1772142,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"男人有結婚目標, 但冇錢冇事業, 女人咪一樣唔吼, 講到尾, 心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f84552d4f3f4232e7e81345870bf03e8a351a0","tid":1772142,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"32"},{"pid":"14fa2afa838520c04390c48944a15e06e8a73738","tid":1772142,"uid":80215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"20歲已經玩夠，<br />\n男人真係可以好遲先定。"},{"pid":"8c24a678cc6fb11e593fcf77563959b94026b0af","tid":1772142,"uid":304228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"遇到啱嘅人就會想<br />\n<br />\n利申：29 歲剛失戀半年⋯"}]}